      "translation": "AIA China entered 2021 with successful momentum, with VONB in the first two months recording very strong growth compared to the same period in 2020. VONB of US$968 million in 2020 was 17% lower than in 2019, primarily due to limited sales in the initial outbreak of COVID-19 in the first quarter. New business momentum improved rapidly as movement restrictions eased. VONB resumed our customary seasonal pattern, with greater weighting towards the first half of the year. In 2020, AIA China was the largest contributor to the Group's VONB."
